data.description: ***SELLER WILL REPLACE ROOF WITH AN ACCEPTED OFFER***Welcome home! This 5 Bedroom, 4 Bath Home, 2 car garage with 4036 square feet on a Corner Lot is located in Apopka, Florida. Step inside and be greeted by an open and inviting layout that seamlessly connects the formal dining and office space. The home's design maximizes both open concept Living Room space with natural light, creating an atmosphere of warmth and comfort. The modern open kitchen, adorned with wood cabinetry, granite countertops, double oven and stainless steel appliances. Whether you are a seasoned chef or just enjoy preparing meals, this kitchen provides the space and amenities for family and friends. The adjacent breakfast nook is perfect for casual dining. Master Bedroom with soaking tub and separate shower complete the downstairs. Upstairs you walk into an oversized LOFT area, THEATER Room , additional four bedrooms are generously sized, each with its own unique character and ample closet space. 2 of the bedrooms are jack in Jill styled with an adjacent craft or FLEX room. There are well-appointed bathrooms throughout the home offer convenience and style. Outdoors you will find a screened in lanai that allows entry into a bathroom, living room and primary bedroom. Nestled in this desirable Apopka neighborhood is close proximity to local parks, New Publix shopping center, dining options, entertainment venues and major highways.
